      <h2> Services </h2>
        <p><i> Past, Present, Future Spreads - $5.00</i></p>
      <p> This is the most basic spread, quick and to the point! It is meant for querents that are seeking to know more about their current situation. </p>
        <p><i>Celtic Cross Spreads - $20.00</i></p>
      <p> A far more exploratory spread, it often takes upwards of 60 minutes to complete. The Celtic Cross focuses on an individual's fated outcome and best outcome. <br> Through 10 random cards, the querent is led to examine the different factors deciding their fate and how best to conduct them!</p>
        <p><i>Specialty Spreads - Prices Varies per Spread</i></p>
      <p> We offer multiple spread types on a case-by-case basis. These spreads focus on issues such as love, attachment, health, opportunities, and much more! <br> Let us know what you are seeking and we are quite likely to have something to match the need.  </p>
    <p><strong> You can book Atticus on <a href="https://squareup.com/appointments/book/2NW86H5MSMS2E/reliquary"> Square</a> or contact them at ADKirkham42@gmail.com!</strong></p>
